eName":"大淘宝技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_8fbe16d8","title":"多维创新打造强泛化智能体模型，LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601 技术报告发布","link":"https://tech.meituan.com/2026/02/02/longcat-flash-thinking-2601-techreport.html","date":"2026-02-02 00:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8fbe16d8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"美团技术团队","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_2744842f","title":"2026-02-05 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-05-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-05 08:48:51","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2744842f.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":73,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_585f577d","title":"今年都在求「健康福」，我测完这个 AI 后决定直接转发家庭群","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654064?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-04 17:00:28","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度测评了垂直医疗 AI“蚂蚁阿福”，阐述其如何通过权威语料、临床诊疗逻辑及生态服务集成，解决通用 AI 在健康咨询中专业度不足、缺乏记忆及无法连接服务等痛点。","summary":"本文是对蚂蚁集团推出的医疗垂直领域 AI 智能体“蚂蚁阿福”的深度测评。文章通过对比通用大模型，详细分析了阿福在医疗场景下的核心优势：首先是专业性，其语料库由数百家医院及名医背书，遵循循证医学原则，显著降低了 AI 幻觉；其次是交互逻辑，阿福模拟了真实医生的“追问-排查”思维，而非简单的单次问答；再者是记忆能力，通过健康档案功能实现了对家庭成员健康数据的长期动态跟踪。此外，文章强调了阿福与支付宝生态的深度集成，使其能够直接提供挂号、医保码调用等实操服务，完成了从信息咨询到医疗服务的闭环。作者认为，这种具备专业性、同理心且能连接服务的垂直 AI，是目前最适合家庭健康管理的工具之一。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_585f577d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":14,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_b57c3f8d","title":"Genie 3 引发游戏股暴跌，但游戏的真正灵魂 AI 永远得不到","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654197?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-04 13:44:27","oneSentenceSummary":"本文深度剖析了 Google Genie 3 引发游戏股暴跌背后的认知误区，指出 AI 的概率性生成无法取代游戏引擎的确定性逻辑与人类创作者赋予的 IP 灵魂。","summary":"上周 Google DeepMind 发布 Genie 3 后，全球游戏公司股价大幅波动。文章认为这种恐慌源于对 AI 能力的误读：将视觉细节的生成等同于完整世界的构建。Genie 3 本质上是基于概率的“帧生成”模型，缺乏物理引擎的硬编程逻辑和长期一致性，容易出现世界结构崩溃。文章以《荒野大镖客 2》为例，强调游戏的“生命感”源于人类对细节（如电力系统、世界观）的极致雕琢。此外，游戏的核心价值在于数十年积累的 IP 情感寄托，这是 AI 无法在真空中生成的。最终，AI 将成为开发者的“超级画笔”，但创作的灵魂仍掌握在人类手中。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_b57c3f8d.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_cf23725c","title":"2026-02-04 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-04-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-04 08:19:22","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_cf23725c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":68,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_0d2d4723","title":"产业之声 | CES 科技展：中美欧日韩的对比观察和产业趋势","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NTg0NDE1Mw==&mid=2652627729&idx=1&sn=2f69c1efc1dcae6cd842cd7b142d4fe3","date":"2026-02-04 07:56:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_0d2d4723.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"阿里研究院","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":56,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_41fe0f75","title":"2026-02-03 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-03-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-03 08:52:14","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_41fe0f75.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":68,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_fc8fb3b8","title":"喝点 VC｜a16z 应用团队：在如今软件可被快速构建的时代，护城河的重要性反而比以往任何时候都更高","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI4NTgxMDk1NA==&mid=2247513862&idx=1&sn=9a61f2ba2b4fcae7fc16eeef7986a406","date":"2026-02-03 02:54:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_fc8fb3b8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Z Potentials","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":118,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_a9b9791f","title":"AI 干掉 80% App 实录：他用 OpenClaw 40 分钟完成自动修 bug、控制智能家居、通宵监控陌生人","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247625162&idx=2&sn=7a5d0f2560b51b067a8c003eff544b49","date":"2026-02